channel.title: What do you listen to outside of EDM?
channel.description: Name some genres/artists/bands you like that isn't strictly EDM. I've been getting back into this band called The Contortionist, they're a prog metal band. I also like indie jazz, post hardcore, chamber pop, and indie rock.

item.title: What do you listen to outside of EDM?
item.dc:creator: TheRealJFalc
item.description:
Pop punk and rock is what I typically listen to. I do love retro sounding music sometimes (especially soundtracks CAVESTORY @stereofield)

I also like some jazz and jazz-influenced older songs, like Make Me Smile by Chicago.

https://www.youtube.com/embed/NifeiFF2Ufo

I especially love Fall Out Boy and P@td.
